Automate Breach Data Alerting Using LeakCheck API
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Integrate the LeakCheck API for automated breach data monitoring
Develop Python scripts to check emails and domains for data breaches
Implement an email notification system for security alerts
Create an automated monitoring solution with scheduled checks
Apply OSINT techniques for proactive security monitoring
Prerequisites
Before starting this lab, students should have:

Basic Python programming knowledge (functions, classes, file I/O)
Familiarity with Linux command line operations
Understanding of REST APIs and HTTP requests
Basic knowledge of email protocols (SMTP)
