Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: API requests failing with authentication errors

Solution: Verify your API key is correct in config.env and properly loaded
Check that the API key has not expired or exceeded rate limits
Issue: Email notifications not sending

Solution: For Gmail, ensure you're using an App Password, not your regular password
Verify SMTP settings and check firewall rules allow outbound port 587
Test with a simple SMTP connection first
Issue: Script stops after first check in monitor mode

Solution: Ensure the while loop in start_monitoring() is properly implemented
Check for exceptions that might be terminating the script
Review logs in breach_monitor.log for error messages
